23/11/2009
TIRANA, Albania -- Police arrested a man Saturday (November 21st) in Mamurras, northwest Albania, with 23.5 kilos of heroin in his possession. The operation, in the home of Hamit Doci, 64, was conducted after police received an anonymous tip. Authorities say they also found weapons in the house. (NOA, Ora News, Telegrafi - 22/11/09)
